sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant Auth as Supabase Auth
    participant GitHub as GitHub API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant EdgeFn as generate-infrastructure
    participant Gemini as Gemini API
    participant Worker as Fly.io Worker
    participant AWS as AWS (SST)

    User->>Frontend: 1. Visit App
    Frontend->>Auth: Login Request
    Auth->>GitHub: OAuth Flow
    GitHub-->>Auth: Access Token
    Auth-->>Frontend: Session Cookie

    User->>Frontend: 2. Select Repository
    Frontend->>GitHub: List User Repos
    GitHub-->>Frontend: Repository List
    User->>Frontend: Choose Repo

    User->>Frontend: 3. Describe Infrastructure<br/>"I need Lambda + API"
    Frontend->>EdgeFn: POST /generate-infrastructure
    Note over Frontend,EdgeFn: {conversationHistory, userMessage,<br/>repoName, repoUrl, selectedServices}

    EdgeFn->>Gemini: Generate Code
    Note over EdgeFn,Gemini: System Prompt +<br/>Conversation Context
    Gemini-->>EdgeFn: JSON Response

    EdgeFn->>DB: Save Conversation
    EdgeFn-->>Frontend: {message, sstConfig,<br/>suggestedChanges, iamPolicy}

    Frontend->>Frontend: Display Chat Message
    Frontend->>Frontend: Show Code in Tabs

    User->>Frontend: 4. Review & Deploy
    Frontend->>EdgeFn: POST /deploy-project
    EdgeFn->>Worker: Queue Deployment Job
    Worker->>AWS: sst deploy --stage production
    AWS-->>Worker: Deployment Result
    Worker-->>Frontend: Status Update
    Frontend-->>User: Show Deploy URL
